data.description: Entertaining Offers Between $450,000 and $485,000. Hard to Find a 2 Bedroom Condo in this Price Range with A) Two Full Baths B) FHA & VA Appoved C) Garage with Storage D) Central Heat & A/C E) Laundry Room in Unit F) Lots Natural Light with Newer Windows, G) Outdoor Patio, often with Colorful Views at Sunset. This Spacious Home has a Good Size Living Room with Fireplace, a Breakfast Nook for Dining, Tile floors, Stainless Steel Appliances and Granite Counter Tops and Larger Bedrooms, with no one living above. Centrally Located, just a Short Drive to National City Golf Course, Restaurants, Shopping Centers, Freeways, Military Bases, Downtown SD, Mexico and Walking Distance to the Elementarty School and Park. Nice Size View Balcony plus a Huge 1 Car Garage (20x8.5) with an additional area (9x8.5) that can be used for more storage, an office, a workout room, etc. You also get the assigned parking space in front of garage.
